        "collapsible_row_b44n9F": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Why are our perfumes so affordable?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p><br/>We invest in the essentials: the fragrance.<br/><br/>No luxurious bottle, no superfluous packaging, no expensive boutiques or overpriced influencer partnerships — to offer you a high-end scent without breaking the bank.<br/></p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_rCVDnP": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Is this eau de parfum?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>Yes, it's an eau de parfum – it contains up to 19% essence. Eau de toilette, for example, contains between 5 and 8% essence, and essence concentration is 41% and more.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_rNbx6p": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Is this an eau de parfum?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p><br/>Yes. Our formula contains up to 19% aromatic concentration.</p><p><br/>For comparison, an Eau de Toilette generally contains between 5 and 8%, while perfume extract starts from 41%.<br/><br/></p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_irweNa": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Does your inspired perfume smell different from the original?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>Not at all. Our inspired fragrances are carefully crafted to recreate a very close olfactory experience: same note family, same depth and same longevity — at a fraction of the price.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_gJVQkB": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What does a 19% perfume concentration mean?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>This corresponds to the amount of pure perfume oils present in each bottle.<br/><br/>With 19%, our perfumes fall fully into the Eau de Parfum category, generally between 16 and 21% concentration. In other words, you enjoy an intensely concentrated fragrance, with longevity comparable to the market's leading references.<br/></p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        }
      },
